1. On se *pretvorio* u pravog umetnika. (He turned into a true artist.)
2. *Pretvorio* je novac u evre. (He converted the money into euros.)
3. Zbog bolesti, morao je da se *pretvori* u vegetarijanca. (Due to illness, he had to become a vegetarian.)
4. Nakon mnogo rada, konačno se *pretvorila* u uspešnu poslovnu ženu. (After a lot of hard work, she finally turned into a successful businesswoman.)
5. Ova igračka se *pretvara* u robota. (This toy transforms into a robot.)
6. *Pretvaranje* novca u drugu valutu nije uvek isplativo. (Converting money into another currency is not always profitable.)
7. Oni su se *pretvarali* da su glavni krivci nevini. (They pretended to be innocent even though they were the main culprits.)
8. Našli su način da *pretvore* staru zgradu u moderan poslovni prostor. (They found a way to convert an old building into a modern business space.)
9. Ova vrsta baterija se može *pretvoriti* u opasni otpad. (This type of battery can be transformed into hazardous waste.)
10. Zbog stresa i pritiska na poslu, počeo je da se *pretvara* da je srećan i zadovoljan. (Due to stress and pressure at work, he started pretending to be happy and satisfied.)